<s-1 id="RM000000YXB00FX_01_0003" proc-id="RM0250U___00000SL00000">
<ptxt>INSPECT FRONT OIL PUMP AND GEAR BODY SUB-ASSEMBLY</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Using a dial indicator, measure the inside diameter of the oil pump body bushing.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="D003648" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<spec>
<title>Standard inside diameter</title>
<specitem>
<ptxt>38.113 to 38.138 mm (1.50051 to 1.50149 in.)</ptxt>
</specitem>
<subtitle>Maximum inside diameter</subtitle>
<specitem>
<ptxt>38.188 mm (1.50346 in.)</ptxt>
</specitem>
</spec>
<ptxt>If the inside diameter is greater than the maximum, replace the oil pump body sub-assembly.</ptxt>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
<s-1 id="RM000000YXB00FX_01_0004" proc-id="RM0250U___00000SM00000">
<ptxt>INSPECT STATOR SHAFT ASSEMBLY</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Using a dial indicator, measure the inside diameter of the stator shaft.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="D003653" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<spec>
<title>Standard inside diameter</title>
<specitem>
<ptxt>21.500 to 21.526 mm (0.84646 to 0.84748 in.)</ptxt>
</specitem>
<subtitle>Maximum inside diameter</subtitle>
<specitem>
<ptxt>21.57 mm (0.8492 in.)</ptxt>
</specitem>
</spec>
<ptxt>If the inside diameter is greater than the maximum, replace the stator shaft.</ptxt>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
</subpara>
</para>
